which was really fun. There's a Japanese
version of this movie if you want to make

00:05:18.980 --> 00:05:23.900
which is really cool.
Can you teach us something in Japanese?

00:05:23.900 --> 00:05:33.200
Oh gosh you know, I learned the lines,
I know some typical greetings -

